name: 维特·蒙雷尔 Yvette Monreal
movies: 第一滴血5：最后的血 Rambo: Last Blood
intro: Actress Yvette Monreal has been featured in the film Off the Grid, MTV’s Awkward, as well as several short films, web series and commercials. Currently Yvette is playing Senna Galan in Bob Orci and Alex Kurtzman’s Matador, for Robert Rodriguez’s El Rey Network. Senna is the cute trouble-making only child of Andres Galan, played by Alfred Molina. Yvette is a graduate of the Stella Adler Art of Acting Conservatory in Los Angeles, CA.
